1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,899
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,900 --> 00:00:32,339
=Episode 9=
(Don't let the past destroy you.)

3
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:34,907
(Sometimes, it's better to let it go.)

4
00:00:54,740 --> 00:00:56,540
Those who return to their cells

5
00:00:57,700 --> 00:00:58,900
will be spared.

6
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:05,060
I am Pei Xiao.

7
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:06,699
Forgive my offense

8
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:08,100
at Baihua Hall.

9
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,180
I've placed a restriction here.

10
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,460
The Flower Slaves outside can't enter.

11
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:15,100
But if mortals come,

12
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,100
you'll have to handle them yourselves.

13
00:01:19,460 --> 00:01:20,580
Thank you, Immortal.

14
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:24,619
Baobao, it's New Year's Eve tonight.

15
00:01:24,620 --> 00:01:26,180
Stay for the feast before you go.

16
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,580
Master,

17
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:31,580
I want to join the New Year's feast.

18
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:36,180
Let's go together.

19
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,740
Why so shy?

20
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,380
Come with me.

21
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:46,660
You too. Come join us.

22
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:51,220
Dad, look at this!

23
00:01:51,260 --> 00:01:53,579
Looks like
the Pei family line is secured!

24
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,100
Chengjiang.

25
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:57,419
Find me one too then.

26
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:58,300
Alright.

27
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:02,300
Come, I'll pour you a drink.

28
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:05,779
Okay, it's full now.

29
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:06,699
Please drink.

30
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,300
Let's raise a toast.

31
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:12,339
May every year bring blessings and joy.

32
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:14,859
Together, we welcome the new year.

33
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,020
Cheers!

34
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,940
Okay.

35
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,859
We'll step away for a bit.

36
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:26,940
Let us know if you need anything.

37
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,300
Just let us know.

38
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:29,199
Let's go.

39
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:31,139
(Lingyun Pavilion)

40
00:02:31,140 --> 00:02:32,300
My Lady,

41
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:33,859
I saw mortals playing a drinking game

42
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:36,020
in the street two days ago.

43
00:02:36,060 --> 00:02:36,979
Lose, and you drink.

44
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:37,979
Do you know this game?

45
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:39,180
Rock, paper, and scissors?

46
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,739
I used to play that with Mother.

47
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,659
Let's see if you can beat me.

48
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:47,139
Come on.

49
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,020
Come.

50
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:50,020
Rock, paper, scissors.

51
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,900
Rock, paper, scissors.

52
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,140
Drink!

53
00:02:58,180 --> 00:02:59,259
Since you're in high spirits,

54
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,900
allow me to entertain with some moves.

55
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:04,299
Again.

56
00:03:04,300 --> 00:03:06,460
Rock, paper, scissors.

57
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:07,740
It's a draw.

58
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:09,620
Let's drink.

59
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:19,900
Rock.

60
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:21,260
Rock.

61
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:24,620
(Ye Zhao,)

62
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:27,460
(you've grown feelings
in a sea of hatred.)

63
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,139
(Have you forgotten how you died)

64
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:30,580
(in your past life?)

65
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,460
(I haven't forgotten.)

66
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:36,060
(But I also remember how I was reborn.)

67
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:40,500
(Will you not avenge
being devoured alive?)

68
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,859
(Will you not end
the demon heart's calamity?)

69
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,860
(Will you not protect the people?)

70
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,780
(Don't make me choose.)

71
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:48,180
(This time,)

72
00:03:48,460 --> 00:03:50,419
(I'll protect)

73
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:51,659
(Xi, Baobao,)

74
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:53,060
(and all living beings.)

75
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,900
(And how will you do that?)

76
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:56,979
(You're nothing)

77
00:03:56,980 --> 00:03:59,260
(but a fool lost in love.)

78
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,699
(I may be a fool)

79
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,300
(but my love is not.)

80
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,939
My Lady, you win.

81
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:16,740
I'll cut you some pig's ear.

82
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,300
Ye Zhao,

83
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:25,300
let's drink.

84
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:31,300
Why are you sweating so much?

85
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:32,980
Are you alright?

86
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,620
Maybe

87
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:37,860
the wine's too strong.

88
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:40,900
Your alcohol tolerance is that low?

89
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:42,459
Drink.

90
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:44,740
I said the wine's strong,

91
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:47,020
not that I'm drunk.

92
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:49,180
General Pei,

93
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:52,260
I'll drink this first.

94
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:54,379
Nice.

95
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:56,060
I'll drink with you to the death.

96
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,620
Lightweight.

97
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:12,620
You...

98
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:17,460
are already drunk?

99
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,299
Everyone's had enough?

100
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,620
Go on.

101
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:22,859
Just keep going, you two.

102
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,259
One more round.

103
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:26,700
Rock, paper, scissors.

104
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:28,499
Let's drink more.

105
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,460
Let's go.

106
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:30,819
Scissors!

107
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:33,059
This is nothing.

108
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:33,619
Alright.

109
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,900
Slow down.

110
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:35,940
Slow down.

111
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:38,260
Then I'll...

112
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:41,740
A swing?

113
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,700
I want to swing.

114
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:59,140
(Even drunk,)

115
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:01,139
(she's just like before.

116
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:03,379
Back in the palace,

117
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:05,180
I always wished

118
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:08,059
someone would give me a push
on the swing.

119
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:09,500
Mother

120
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,620
was always at war.

121
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,940
The Emperor

122
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,300
always ignored me.

123
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:20,820
Only one Golden-Masked Guard

124
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:23,380
ever pushed me a few times.

125
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:28,500
The others feared me,

126
00:06:28,620 --> 00:06:32,180
said I was a cursed child.

127
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:34,580
No one liked me.

128
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,380
I...

129
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,700
finally learned

130
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:44,620
to love myself.

131
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:48,299
Just because my eyes glow red

132
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:50,500
and I can see life and death,

133
00:06:50,740 --> 00:06:52,620
the Emperor threw me in prison

134
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:55,140
without a word.

135
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,500
Once,

136
00:06:57,820 --> 00:06:59,419
he said

137
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:00,500
in front of everyone

138
00:07:01,260 --> 00:07:03,020
that he'd gouge out my eyes.

139
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:07,060
My own father

140
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:11,260
wanted to gouge out my eyes.

141
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:25,380
If you want to cry, then cry.

142
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,260
No one's here.

143
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:32,020
I...

144
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:35,700
What are you saying?

145
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:38,300
I'm telling you a joke.

146
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:40,620
Don't you find it funny?

147
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:52,060
After I met you,

148
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,620
I realized something.

149
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,260
You don't have to destroy yourself

150
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:00,700
fighting the past.

151
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,580
Sometimes,

152
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,620
it's better to let it go.

153
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:18,820
Let it go.

154
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:26,020
Just let it go.

155
00:09:32,625 --> 00:09:35,533
Miss, forgive my rudeness.

156
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:39,140
Just call me Baobao.

157
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:40,620
And I am Pei Xiao.

158
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:43,660
Then I'll call you Xiao.

159
00:09:45,162 --> 00:09:47,299
(Martial Hall)

160
00:09:47,300 --> 00:09:48,620
Where is this?

161
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:52,500
The Martial Hall.

162
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:55,900
My father and I trained here
since young.

163
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,620
Where is he now?

164
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:13,260
He passed when I was young.

165
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:19,740
I'm sorry.

166
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:22,500
Did your father give you that mask?

167
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:27,980
In the Pei family,

168
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,299
the heir does not weep at mourning.

169
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,899
That day, Her Highness used this mask

170
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:34,620
to preserve my family's dignity.

171
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:38,380
I've worn it ever since.

172
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:40,659
So what if you cry?

173
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:41,579
If you ask me,

174
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:43,699
I'd say just cry and laugh
whenever you want.

175
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:45,340
Who cares about dignity?

176
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,540
Smile.

177
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:53,620
No, like this.

178
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:03,620
General, you can do it.

179
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:06,140
Father,

180
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:08,059
just look at them.

181
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:09,620
He's not very imposing.

182
00:11:09,940 --> 00:11:11,059
Why not climb the roof?

183
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:12,260
Up on the roof,

184
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,219
he'd stand

185
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,059
above it all,

186
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:15,419
with everything beneath him.

187
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,819
The roof?

188
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:19,339
He's drunk and you wanted him
to climb the roof?

189
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,659
if he falls,

190
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:21,419
it's on you.

191
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,500
I...

192
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,260
Continue!

193
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:27,419
Xiao, let's go find My Lady.

194
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,539
Oh no! Let's go!

195
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:30,620
My Lady!

196
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,860
My Lady!

197
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:44,939
I want to buy Pei Xiao a gift.

198
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:47,540
I broke the mask you gave him.

199
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:52,020
Alright.

200
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,459
It's New Year's Eve today.

201
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:55,059
The night market must be lively.

202
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:55,980
Let's go.

203
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:57,260
Let's go.

204
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,699
Your Highness, outside...

205
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:01,740
Hey, you!

206
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:04,500
Give me a hand.

207
00:12:10,820 --> 00:12:12,140
Let them go.

208
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:14,780
We'll follow in secret.

209
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,540
Agreed.

210
00:12:45,430 --> 00:12:47,139
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

211
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:49,989
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

212
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:52,729
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

213
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:54,359
♪Let the long shadows♪

214
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:59,960
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

215
00:13:00,010 --> 00:13:01,609
♪If in a dream♪

216
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:04,369
♪I can hear your voice♪

217
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:07,219
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

218
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,819
♪Let it be us♪

219
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:14,609
♪drawing endlessly close♪

220
00:13:14,610 --> 00:13:16,369
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

221
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:19,020
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

222
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:21,959
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

223
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,609
♪Not even in time♪

224
00:13:23,610 --> 00:13:29,269
♪to tell you how I feel♪

225
00:13:29,270 --> 00:13:30,809
♪If the rain won't stop♪

226
00:13:30,810 --> 00:13:33,559
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

227
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:36,529
♪Let love go on♪

228
00:13:36,530 --> 00:13:39,079
♪Until forever♪

229
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:43,719
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

230
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:46,329
♪Until forever♪

231
00:13:46,330 --> 00:13:53,440
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
